          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Da, merita daca vrei sa ai control total asupra ingredientelor, sa te bucuri de paine proaspata si aromata zilnic si sa economisesti pe termen lung. O masina premium de la branduri consacrate garanteaza calitate si durabilitate, facand-o o investitie buna.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          ce masina de paine premium e cea mai buna
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Cele mai bune masini de paine premium sunt adesea modelele de la Panasonic (ex: SD-YR2500) si Kenwood (ex: BM450). Panasonic exceleaza prin functiile smart si dispenserul automat, in timp ce Kenwood impresioneaza prin robustete si <a href="/laptop-gaming-performant/">performant</a>a pura.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          ce programe sunt esentiale la o masina de paine premium
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Programele esentiale includ Paine Alba, Paine Integrala si Program Rapid. Functii precum programarea intarziata, controlul crustei si optiuni pentru paine fara gluten sau aluaturi sunt, de asemenea, foarte utile la o masina premium.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          cum intretin o masina de paine premium
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Pentru a intretine o masina de paine premium, curata cuva si tamburul dupa fiecare utilizare cu un burete moale si detergent. Evita materialele abrazive. Sterge carcasa cu o carpa umeda. Depoziteaza-o intr-un loc uscat si ferit de umezeala.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          unde gasesc masini de paine premium la oferta
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Poti gasi masini de paine premium la oferta in marile magazine de electronice din Romania, atat fizic cat si online (eMAG, Altex, Flanco). De asemenea, verifica site-urile oficiale ale brandurilor sau platformele de comparare a preturilor.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          ce probleme pot aparea la o masina de paine premium
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Problemele frecvente, chiar si la masinile premium, pot include necoacerea uniforma a crustei, painea care nu creste suficient (din cauza drojdiei sau a fainii gresite) sau probleme cu tamburul de framantare. Respectarea retetelor si a instructiunilor reduce aceste riscuri.</div>
      </div>
